title: Gabrielle Union & Jimmy Fallon Do the Morning Announcements as Nerdy Principals - Watch Now!
text: Gabrielle Union and Jimmy Fallon dress up as super nerdy school principals to make some morning announcements during The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon on Monday (October 12) in New York City . The pair kept parodying famous songs, including OMI‘s “Cheerleader,” Rihanna‘s “Bitch Better Have My Money,” The Weeknd‘s “Can’t Feel My Face,” and more. [...] »
